\c 28
\s Nguvo dzeMupristi Mukuru
\p
\v 1 Zvino iwe uswededze kwauri Aroni mukoma wako, nevanakomana vake pamwe naye kubva pakati pevana vaIsraeri, kuti andishumire paupristi: Aroni, Nadhabhi, naAbhihu, Ereazari, naItamari, vanakomana vaAroni.
\v 2 Uitire Aroni mukoma wako nguvo tsvene dzerukudzo uye dzerunako.
\v 3 Ugotaure iwe kuna vese vane moyo yakachenjera, vandakazadza nemweya weuchenjeri, kuti vaite nguvo dzaAroni dzekumuita mutsvene, kuti andishumire paupristi.
\v 4 Nguvo dzavachaita ndidzo: Hombodo yechipfuva, neefodhi, nejazi, nenguvo refu yakarukwa, nguwani, nebhanhire; zvino ngavaitire Aroni, mukoma wako, nevanakomana vake nguvo tsvene, kuti andishumire paupristi.
\v 5 Ivo ngavatorewo goridhe, nezveruvara rwedenga, nezveruvara rwehute, nezvitsuku, nemucheka wakaisvonaka.
\p
\v 6 Efodhi ngavaiite negoridhe, zveruvara rwedenga, nezveruvara rwehute, zvitsvuku, nemucheka wakaisvonaka wakarukwa, basa remusoni.
\v 7 Ngaive mapandi emafudzi maviri akabatanidza pamicheto yayo miviri kuti ibatanidzwe.
\v 8 Nebhanhire reefodhi yaro, riri pamusoro payo, richava sebasa rayo, kubva pairi, negoridhe, zveruvara rwedenga, nezveruvara rwehute, nezvitsvuku, nemucheka wakaisvonaka wakarukwa.
\v 9 Utorewo mabwe maviri eonikisi, ugofombora paari mazita evanakomana vaIsraeri;
\v 10 matanhatu emazita avo pabwe rimwe, matanhatu emazita avo akasara pabwe rimwe, zvichienderana nekuberekwa kwavo.
\v 11 \add Se\add*basa remufombori wemabwe, sekufomborwa kwezvidhindo, uchaafombora mabwe aya maviri mazita evanakomana vaIsraeri, uchaaita anyure muzvirukwa zvegoridhe.
\v 12 Zvino uchaisa mabwe ayo maviri pamapandi emafudzi eefodhi, \add ave\add* mabwe echirangaridzo kuvana vaIsraeri; naAroni achatakura mazita awo pamberi paJehovha pamafudzi ake maviri, chive chirangaridzo.
\p
\v 13 Zvino uchaita zvirukwa zvegoridhe,
\v 14 neketani mbiri dzegoridhe rakazara; uzviite zvakamonwa, basa rakakoshwa; maketani akakoshwa uasungire pazvirukwa izvo.
\p
\v 15 Uchaitawo hombodo yechipfuva yekutonga, rive basa remhizha; uiite sebasa reefodhi; negoridhe, zveruvara rwedenga, nezveruvara rwehute, nezvitsvuku, nemucheka wakarukwa wakaisvonaka uchachiita.
\v 16 Ngaienzane mativi mana yakapetwa kaviri; kureba kwayo chiri chanza; uye kureba kwayo kuve chanza.
\v 17 Uchaisawo mairi zvitanga zvemabwe zvinokosha, misara mina yemabwe; musara wesadhiosi, topasi, nekabhunakeri; musara wekutanga.
\v 18 Nemusara wechipiri emaradhi, safiri, nedhaimani.
\v 19 Nemusara wechitatu hiakindi, agati, neametisiti.
\v 20 Nemusara wechina bheriri, neonikisi, nejasiperi. Zvicharukwa negoridhe muzvitanga zvazvo.
\v 21 Zvino mabwe achava nemazita evanakomana vaIsraeri, ari gumi nemaviri zvichienderana nemazita avo; akafomborwa pazvidhindo, umwe ibwe neumwe ibwe nezita rake rebwe; achava kumarudzi gumi nemaviri.
\p
\v 22 Zvino uchaita pahombodo yechipfuva maketani akamonwa basa rakamonwa regoridhe rakazara.
\v 23 Uchaitawo pahombodo yechipfuva zvindori zviviri zvegoridhe, uye uchaisa zvindori zviviri pamicheto miviri yehombodo yechipfuva.
\v 24 Zvino uchaisa \add ketani\add* dzakamonwa dzegoridhe muzvindori zviviri pamicheto yehombodo yechipfuva.
\v 25 Nemicheto miviri ye\add ketani\add* mbiri dzakamonwa uchasungira muzvirukwa zviviri, zvino uzviise pamapandi emafudzi eefodhi mhiri pakatarisana nayo.
\p
\v 26 Uchaitawo zvindori zviviri zvegoridhe, ugozviisa pamicheto miviri yehombodo yechipfuva pamupendero wayo uri kune rimwe divi reefodhi mukati.
\v 27 Uchaitawo zvindori zviviri zvegoridhe, ugozviisa pamapandi emafudzi maviri eefodhi zasi nechemberi kwayo, pedo payakabatanidzwa napo, pamusoro pebhanhire reefodhi.
\v 28 Zvino vachasunga hombodo yechipfuva nezvindori zvayo pazvindori zveefodhi nerwonzi rweruvara rwedenga, kuti ruve pamusoro pebhanhire reefodhi, uye hombodo yechipfuva irege kubva paefodhi.
\v 29 Naizvozvo Aroni achatakura mazita evana vaIsraeri pahombodo yechipfuva yekutonga pamoyo wake, kana achipinda munzvimbo tsvene, chive chirangaridzo pamberi paJehovha nguva dzese.
\p
\v 30 Uchaisawo Urimi neTumimi muhombodo yechipfuva yekutonga, zvino zvichava pamoyo waAroni kana achipinda pamberi paJehovha; naAroni achatakura kutongwa kwevana vaIsraeri pamoyo wake pamberi paJehovha nguva dzese.
\p
\v 31 Uchaitawo jazi reefodhi rese neruvara rwedenga.
\v 32 Zvino pachava neburi remusoro waro pakati paro; richava nemupendero webasa rakarukwa rakapoteredza buri raro, rive seburi renguvo yejazi reutare, \add kuti\add* rirege kubvaruka.
\p
\v 33 Uchaitawo pamupendero waro mapomegiranati* ezveruvara rwedenga, nezveruvara rwehute nezvitsvuku anopoteredza pamupendero waro, nemadare egoridhe pakati pawo akapoteredza.
\v 34 Dare regoridhe nepomegiranati, dare regoridhe nepomegiranati pamupendero wejazi wakapoteredza.
\v 35 Zvino zvichava panaAroni kushumira, kuti kurira kwaro kunzwike paanopinda munzvimbo tsvene pamberi paJehovha, nepakubuda kwake, kuti asafa.
\p
\v 36 Zvino uchaita hwandefa regoridhe rakazara, ugofombora pariri, \add se\add*pakafomborwa pezvidhindo \add uchiti:\add* UTSVENE KUNA JEHOVHA.
\v 37 Uchariisawo parwonzi rweruvara rwedenga, rigoiswa pangundu, rive mhiri pakatarisana nengundu.
\v 38 Zvino richava pahuma yaAroni, kuti Aroni atakure kuipa kwezvinhu zvitsvene, vana vaIsraeri zvavachaita zvitsvene pazvipo zvavo zvitsvene zvese; uye richava pahuma yake nguva dzese, kuti vagamuchirwe pamberi paJehovha.
\p
\v 39 Ucharukawo nguvo refu yemucheka wakaisvonaka, uye uchaita ngundu yemucheka wakaisvonaka, uye uchaita bhanhire nebasa rechirukwa.
\p
\v 40 Nevanakomana vaAroni uchavaitira nguvo refu, uye uchavaitira mabhanhire, uvaitirewo ngowani, zvive rukudzo nerunako.
\v 41 Zvino uchazvipfekedza Aroni mukoma wako nevanakomana vake pamwe naye; uye uchavazodza, nekuvaeresa, nekuvaita vatsvene, kuti vandishumire paupristi.
\v 42 Uchavaitirawo zvikadubura zvemukati zvemucheka kufukidza nyama yakashama; zvichava kubva pazviuno kusvika pachidya.
\v 43 Zvichapfekwawo naAroni nevanakomana vake pakupinda kwavo mutende rekusangana, kana pavanoswedera paaritari kushumira panzvimbo tsvene; kuti varege kutakura chakaipa vakafa. Chive chimiso narinhi narinhi kwaari nekumbeu yake shure kwake.